Package org.openqa.selenium.remote

Interface AugmenterProvider<X>

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AddApplicationCache, AddLocationContext, AddNetworkConnection, AddRotatable, AddWebStorage, DevToolsProvider
    public interface AugmenterProvider<X>
    Describes and provides an implementation for a particular interface for use with the Augmenter. Think of this as a simulacrum of mixins.
